{% extends "base/email_base.txt.j2" %}

{% block content %}
Payment Reminder

This is a friendly reminder that you have an outstanding invoice.

Invoice Summary:
- Invoice Number: #{{ invoice_number }}
- Amount Due: {{ amount_due_formatted }}
- Due Date: {{ due_date | format_date }}
- Status: {{ status | upper }}

